Interface ChangeNoticeComplexityDelegate

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultChangeNoticeComplexityDelegate
    Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public interface ChangeNoticeComplexityDelegate
    This is the interface which defines the delegate to be implemented to calculate the complexity of the Change Notice.

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: true

    @deprecated use ChangeItemComplexityDelegate instead.
